    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>tofu</strong>, and cut the block in half then each half in half again on a diagonal</p><p>Pat the <strong>tofu pieces </strong>dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Sprinkle both sides of the <strong>tofu</strong> <strong>pieces</strong> with <strong>flour</strong> until fully coated, then tap off any excess</p>",
