    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, reboil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the reserved pot, cover them with<strong> boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through, then drain and return to the pot with a small knob of<strong> butter alternative</strong> and pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mash the peas until they come together nicely – these are your <strong>mushy peas</strong></p>",
